name: Just Dance: Disney Party 2
overview: Just Dance: Disney Party 2 is a game in the Just Dance series published by Ubisoft. It is the sequel to Just Dance: Disney Party and was released on October 20, 2015. Unlike the previous game, Just Dance: Disney Party 2 only features songs from Disney Channel original movies and shows, which includes songs from Austin & Ally, Descendants, Teen Beach 2, Liv and Maddie, Violetta, Girl Meets World and many more.
